---
// Header component — hero section with title + lang switch
---
<header class="hero" data-pagefind-ignore>
  <h1>MITE: Break Everything</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">
    <span data-lang="hu">Nem hivatalos wiki a MITE: Break Everything modhoz</span>
    <span data-lang="en">Unofficial wiki for the MITE: Break Everything mod</span>
    <span data-lang="ru">Неофициальная вики для мода MITE: Break Everything</span>
  </p>
  <p class="dev-notice">
    <span data-lang="hu">
      <span class="dev-notice-full">⚠️ Ez a wiki folyamatos fejlesztés alatt áll — egyes adatok pontatlanok vagy hiányosak lehetnek. Ha hibát találsz, <a href="https://github.com/TornadoGamesNow/mite-be-wiki/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">jelezd GitHub Issue-ban</a>!</span>
      <span class="dev-notice-short">⚠️ Wiki WIP — <a href="https://github.com/TornadoGamesNow/mite-be-wiki/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hiba jelzése</a></span>
    </span>
    <span data-lang="en">
      <span class="dev-notice-full">⚠️ This wiki is a work in progress — some data may be inaccurate or incomplete. If you spot an error, please <a href="https://github.com/TornadoGamesNow/mite-be-wiki/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">report it as a GitHub Issue</a>!</span>
      <span class="dev-notice-short">⚠️ Wiki WIP — <a href="https://github.com/TornadoGamesNow/mite-be-wiki/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">report issue</a></span>
    </span>
    <span data-lang="ru">
      <span class="dev-notice-full">⚠️ Эта вики находится в разработке — некоторые данные могут быть неточными или неполными. Если найдёте ошибку, пожалуйста <a href="https://github.com/TornadoGamesNow/mite-be-wiki/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">сообщите об этом через GitHub Issue</a>!</span>
      <span class="dev-notice-short">⚠️ Вики в разработке — <a href="https://github.com/TornadoGamesNow/mite-be-wiki/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">сообщить об ошибке</a></span>
    </span>
  </p>
  <div class="lang-switch">
    <button class="lang-btn active" data-set-lang="hu">Magyar</button>
    <button class="lang-btn" data-set-lang="en">English</button>
    <button class="lang-btn" data-set-lang="ru">Русский</button>
  </div>
</header>

<script is:inline>
  document.querySelectorAll('[data-set-lang]').forEach(function(btn) {
    btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
      var lang = this.getAttribute('data-set-lang');
      document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-lang-init', lang);
      localStorage.setItem('mite-wiki-lang', lang);
      document.querySelectorAll('.lang-btn').forEach(function(b) { b.classList.remove('active'); });
      this.classList.add('active');
      window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('mite-lang-change', { detail: lang }));
    });
  });
  (function() {
    var lang = document.documentElement.getAttribute('data-lang-init') || 'hu';
    document.querySelectorAll('.lang-btn').forEach(function(b) {
      b.classList.toggle('active', b.getAttribute('data-set-lang') === lang);
    });
  })();
</script>
